The Earnings Trade Strategy automates the process of entering and exiting trades based on earnings announcements for Apple (AAPL). It allows users to take a position—either long (buy) or short (sell short)—on the trading day before an earnings announcement and close that position on the trading day after the announcement. By leveraging TradingView’s Paper Trading environment, the strategy enables users to simulate trades and collect performance data over a 6-month period in a risk-free setting.


